<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ParticipantRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A dataspace-scoped role taken by a participant with respect to AI assets. Anti-rigid: an agent can gain and lose roles over time. Subclasses are intentionally NOT mutually disjoint — one agent can hold several roles simultaneously (e.g., a research group may be both Evaluator and Model Provider)."@en .
<http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Role> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov-o#> .
