<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#AuditEvidence> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A compliance-oriented evidence record attached to a governed activity, carrying a structured SPDX checksum (algorithm + digest), a signer, and a timestamp."@en .
