<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#deploysModel> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links a deployment to the model it serves. Functional: one deployment serves one model. Asymmetric: a deployment and its model are distinct individuals."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#CrossParticipantProvenanceRecord> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A reusable semantic bundle that aggregates prov:Activity and prov:Entity across participant contexts to tell one audit-ready story."@en .
