<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#evidenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Links audit evidence to the activity it attests. Functional. Asymmetric: audit evidence is distinct from the activity it records. Deliberately NOT declared a subproperty of prov:hadActivity: that property is used on reified influence/generation/usage objects, not on entities — an AuditEvidence is a prov:Entity that is ABOUT an activity, which PROV-O does not provide a direct property for."@en .
<http://spdx.org/rdf/terms#checksumValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <http://spdx.org/rdf/terms#Checksum> .
