<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#ExecutionAuthorization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "execution authorization"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pionera/daimo#SharedEvaluationContext> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Two candidate models evaluated on the same SharedEvaluationContext (identical it6:Task, dcat:Dataset, daimo:datasetVersion, daimo:protocol, and daimo:randomSeed) yield metric values that are directly comparable; changing any of the five facets breaks comparability."@en .
